# ğŸ§  Technical Questions Asked

## Q1.
What is Microservices Architecture? Explain its advantages and disadvantages.

## Q2.
In a microservices architecture, how can we centralize and monitor logs from multiple services?

## Q3.
How do you implement Spring Security in a microservices application with role-based authorization?

## Q4.
